response.overview: Featuring soothing sights and melodic sounds, this relaxing video whisks viewers away to the rich underwater world of the Caribbean, the Red Sea and the Indian Ocean for a glimpse into a spectacular aquatic universe. You'll find yourself in healing waters as you marvel at brilliantly colored coral outcroppings, a host of exotic marine creatures and vibrant plant life ... all from the comfort of your armchair.
response.title: Nature States - Sea of Serenity
